questions.text: Esi sicatshulwa sigxile kwintsingiselo yefilosofi yeBlack Consciousness kaSteve Biko ngowe1968.
Le sosi ilandelayo inika ingcaciso yempembelelo yeBlack Consciousness Movement kuveli Mbele owayehlala eSoweto ngowe1976.
Esi sicatshulwa sigxile kwimpembelelo yeBlack Consciousness Movement (BCM) kubafundi beminyaka yowe1970's.
Le yikhathuni eyenziwe nguZapiro ukukhumbuza ngoSteve Biko neyathi yapapashwa kwiDaily Maverick yomhla we19 kweyoMsintsi 2017.
Esi sicatshulwa sichaza izizathu zokuqulunqwa kweTRC yipalamente yokuqala yedemokhrasi ngowe1995.
Esi sicatshulwa sigxile kwizizathu nakwindlela awayetyengwa ngayo uAmy Biehl ngomhla wama25 kweyeThupa 1993 eKapa.
Le sosi igxile ekuveni kweengxelo zababecela uxolelo ngokubulala uAmy Biehl ngomhla we8 kweyeKhala 1997 eKapa.
Le foto ibonisa ababulali bakaAmy Biehl kuvivwongxelo loxolelo lwabo ngomhla we8 kweyeKhala 1997 eKapa.
Le sosi ingezantsi ichaza intsingiselo yeglobalizeyishini.
Le sosi inika ingcaciso ngefuthe leglobalizeyishini kwinkcubeko zamazwe asaphuhlayo.
Esi sicatshulwa singezantsi inika ingcaciso ngendlela olwayiqalazela ngayo inkampani multi-national company, 'Nike,' ngowe1998.
Le powusta ihlasela ookopolotyeni baseWashington D.C. ngowe1998.
